resources.string: Aaditya Shah, the founder of this app named StockCrunch, is a young, talented, and enthusiastic businessman who with the new tactics took his business to a new height. He started his entrepreneurial Journey at the age of 17.

StockCrunch is dedicated to providing you with Top-quality and Informative Videos about the Share/Stock market of Nepal. We have the objective of building financial discipline in the masses by simplifying Stock Market education and Financial concepts.

This application is made for those understudies and experts who need to find out with regards to the securities exchange in the most orderly and pragmatic manner for which no earlier money foundation is required.
